msgid empgren_txt {
text "_Technical Specifications: AEMG M300 Electromagnetic Pulse Grenade

CLASSIFIED LEVEL YELLOW


Overview

The M300 Electromagnetic pulse grenade is designed and produced by AEMG industries based on our research.
It is tailored to defeat the alien drones nicknamed 'bloodspiders' by creating an EMP which overloads the drones' internal circuitry.
Standard composition includes a cylindrical light polymer exterior, a safety-pin and handle, a timed fuse and a core-device,
which produces a high intensity, short duration pulse, fueled by an electrochemical reaction.


Recommended Doctrine

M300 EMP grenade has a short radius of effect and it has no effect on non-electrical entities."
}




